* #### New Eatwell Guide from Public Health England
A new Eatwell Guide has been published tby Public Health England (PHE). The
guide replaces the ‘Eatwell Plate’.A new Eatwell Guide has been published tby
Public Health England (PHE). The guide replaces the ‘Eatwell Plate’.The new
guide, which Diabetes UK supports, says a healthy diet should include more
fruit, vegetables and starchy carbohydrates and have fewer sugary foods and
drinks. Foods high in fat, salt and sugar have been described as ‘foods to eat
less often and in small amounts’.The new guide, which Diabetes UK supports,
